    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spit, Stomp, Smash!</strong></h2></li></ul>Spit on everything that moves. Stomp on farmers' heads or wreak havoc with <i>vomit-o-matic</i> power-up. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144670/extras/07ec920b33cefe961fe1c73baf2f7ead.poster.avif?t=1666430975\" width=578 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144670/extras/07ec920b33cefe961fe1c73baf2f7ead.webm?t=1666430975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144670/extras/07ec920b33cefe961fe1c73baf2f7ead.mp4?t=1666430975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Easy to Begin &amp; Fun to Master</strong></h2></li></ul>Seamless on-boarding thanks to intuitive controls.. and advisor pigs! Discover fun movement tricks (+famous speedrun memes).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144670/extras/ac0393fbe522cc3d9875bc8aa4a8d8b8.avif?t=1666430975\" width=764 height=242 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cozy Atmosphere</strong></h2></li></ul>Hop on top of the clouds or explore deep dungeons and collect shiny gold coins.. but always be cautious! This world is full of hazards such as great voids, fire, lava, electric, angry farmers and two top secret <i>&quot;end-cows&quot;.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144670/extras/32d76dae6017fb008de47d9deb9b2f2e.avif?t=1666430975\" width=754 height=224 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Speedrun</strong></h2></li></ul>Enjoy fast paced movement and its fun quirks. Sharpen your air control, double jump and trick jump skills. Manipulate physics to become the fastest llama in the world!<br><br><i>Note: As a solo-developer, your feedback is valuable to me. You can directly contact me about anything. Thanks for playing my game!</i>",
